Type: Package
Package: dirtywind
Title: Use the HYSPLIT model and tie its results to pollution data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Ivan", "Higuera-Mendieta", email = "ivanhigueram@uchicago.edu",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Use the HYSPLIT model in R, implemented by the splitr package, 
    and add some SQL support and some code to tie the data with pollution data
    to the zip-code level, and more stuff!.
